<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/alex-norris> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Alex Norris was apppointed Minister of State at the Home Office on 6 September 2025. He was previously Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government between 9 July 2024 and 6 September 2025. He has been the MP for Nottingham North and Kimberley (and its predecessor Nottingham North) since June 2017."@en .
